Bates A. Clarke, appellant, v. Illinois Commercial Men’s Association, appellee.Gen. No. 32,510.

Taylor, J., dissents.

Opinion filed June 20, 1928.Rathje, Wesemann, Hinckley & Barnard, for appellant; John Laux, of counsel. Ryan, Condon & Livingston, for appellee; Lowell A. Lawson, of counsel. Mr. Presiding Justice Holdom
